h their own unique cave formations and colorful (sometimes deadly) flora and fauna.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And with 100% destructible environments, you can shape the terrain as you see fit. Dig tunnels, collapse stalagmites and close off choke points to make your job easier.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/548430/extras/98fd5d2f0e24955a536b84a6f9737c16.poster.avif?t=1773067746\" width=1170 height=374 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/548430/extras/98fd5d2f0e24955a536b84a6f9737c16.webm?t=1773067746\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/548430/extras/98fd5d2f0e24955a536b84a6f9737c16.mp4?t=1773067746\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your work in the mines will pit you against the many creatures of Hoxxes IV who don’t take kindly to your presence.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Keep your finger on the trigger, and learn to defend yourself against hordes of over <strong>50 different enemy types</strong>, all of which are keen to bite, slash and acid-spit you to death. Some fly, some crawl, some snatch you from above and below. You’ll need to keep your wits about you, and make sure your teammates have your back.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/548430/extras/e25b9204dd1bd4115bcf1c3ba0183b86.poster.avif?t=1773067746\" width=1170 height=374 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/548430/extras/e25b9204dd1bd4115bcf1c3ba0183b86.webm?t=1773067746\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shar